@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}

<main aria-labelledby="title">
    <header class="about-header">
        <img style="width:100px;height:auto;margin-left:0px" src="~/logo1.png" alt="Alternate Text" />
        <h1 id="title">About</h1>

        <h2><b>Internship Companies Manager</b></h2>
    </header>

    <div class="about-content" style="border:1px solid black; border-radius:10px;">
        <section>
            <h3>Project for Internet Technologies Course</h3>
            <p>
                The "Internship Companies Manager" application is a web solution designed to facilitate
                the management and overview of companies offering student internships. Through this application,
                administrators can easily add, edit, and delete company information, while students (users)
                can simply and quickly browse all available companies, their sectors, contact information,
                and number of open positions.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h3>Application Features</h3>
            <p>
                The application is designed with a clear role division, where "Admin" users have full
                data management rights, while "User" users can only view information, enabling secure
                and controlled interaction. The system uses a modern MVC design pattern that facilitates
                application maintenance and expansion, while the implementation of modern UI technologies
                ensures an intuitive and user-friendly interface.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h3>Practical Application</h3>
            <p>
                This solution is practical and applicable in real situations at faculty or company level,
                enabling better organization and quick information about student internship opportunities,
                making it useful for students, administrators, and companies alike.
            </p>
        </section>
    </div>
</main>



<style>
    .about-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        padding-top: 20px;
        position: relative;
    }

    .logo-container {
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
        width: 150px;
        height: 100px;
    }

    .logo-placeholder {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        border: 1px dashed #ccc;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: #999;
    }

    .about-content {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 50px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        padding: 0 20px;
    }

        .about-content section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .about-content h3 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .about-content p {
            text-align: justify;
        }

    .about-footer {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .footer-content {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
